                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Almost as good as the Intel marketing animations, and they were obsessed not just with branch prediction but out of order execution, both strategies being &quot;speculative&quot;. Reading ahead in memory and storage (sequential pre-fetch to buffer) is also speculative. It all adds up.&lt;/span&gt;

